div.p: Welcome to our SVG map directory! Use the list below to select a map you need. All maps come in two level of details: High and Low.
All maps are available for free for non-commercial use under Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License. For commercial use please consider acquiring an amCharts license.

p.strong: Please note that the maps listed on this page are for legacy reasons, and are not being updated anymore. Some of them might be outdated. Make sure the map is right for you, before using it.
Psssst! Check out our new tool: VisitedPlaces.com. Create cool maps, images, and even videos of your visited countries and visited states!
